==1973&ndash;74==
<!--{{main|Dundee United F.C. season 1973-74}}
-->
The club finished the Division One season in eighth place, again sandwiched between [[Ayr United F.C.|Ayr United]] and [[Motherwell F.C.|Motherwell]]. The club reached their first [[Scottish Cup 1973-74#Final|Scottish Cup Final]] this season, only to be beaten by [[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]]. In the League Cup, the club failed to get past the first round while in the Texaco Cup, United were eliminated in the semi-finals after [[extra time]] by eventual winners [[Newcastle United F.C.|Newcastle United]].<ref name="sfh" />

