==1974&ndash;75==
<!--{{main|Dundee United F.C. season 1974-75}}
-->
The club finished the Division One season in fourth place, in the last season before the formation of the Premier Division. The club were knocked out of the Scottish Cup by Aberdeen for the third time in five years, this time in the [[Scottish Cup 1974-75#Fourth round|fourth round]], while once again United failed to get past the League Cup first round. In the [[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup|Cup Winners Cup]], United were eliminated in the [[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup 1974&ndash;75#Second round|second round]] by [[Turkey|Turkish]] side [[Bursaspor]].

