==1975&ndash;76==
<!--{{main|Dundee United F.C. season 1975-76}}
-->
The club finished the season in eighth place, in the first season of the new Premier Division, avoiding relegation on goal difference. The club were knocked out of the Scottish Cup by [[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]] in the [[Scottish Cup 1975-76#Fourth round|fourth round]] after a replay, while once again United failed to get past the League Cup first round. In the UEFA Cup, United were eliminated in the [[UEFA Cup 1975&ndash;76#Second round|second round]] by [[Portugal|Portuguese]] side [[F.C. Porto|Porto]].

