==1978&ndash;79==
<!--{{main|Dundee United F.C. season 1978-79}}
-->
The club finished the season in third place, finishing just four points behind champions Celtic. The club were knocked out of the Scottish Cup by [[St Mirren F.C.|St Mirren]] in the [[Scottish Cup 1978-79#Third round|third round]], while Celtic knocked United out of the League Cup in the second round. In the UEFA Cup, United were narrowly eliminated in the [[UEFA Cup 1978&ndash;79#First round|first round]] by [[Belgium|Belgian]] side [[Standard Liege]].

