==1979&ndash;80==
<!--{{main|Dundee United F.C. season 1979-80}}
-->
The club finished the season in fourth place, beating Rangers to a UEFA Cup place on goal difference. The club were knocked out of the Scottish Cup by [[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]] in the [[Scottish Cup 1979-80#Fouth round|fourth round]], while the club became League Cup Winners for the first time defeating [[Aberdeen F.C.|Aberdeen]] 3-0 in the Final replay at Dens Park after a goalless draw at Hampden. In the UEFA Cup, United were eliminated in the [[UEFA Cup 1979&ndash;80#Second round|second round]] by [[Hungary|Hungarian]] side [[Diósgyőri VTK]].

