{{infobox country at games | NPC = USA | NPCname = [[United States Paralympic Committee]] | games = Winter Paralympics | year = 1998 | flagcaption = [[Flag of the United States]] | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.teamusa.org/US-Paralympics }} | location = [[Nagano (city)|Nagano]] | competitors = 49 | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = 3 | gold = 13 | silver = 8 | bronze = 13 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[United States]]''' competed at the '''[[1998 Winter Paralympics]]''' in [[Nagano (city)|Nagano]], [[Japan]]. 49 competitors from United States won 34 medals including 13 gold, 8 silver and 13 bronze and finished 3rd in the [[1998 Winter Paralympics medal table|medal table]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org/united-states-america|title=United States of America - National Paralympic Committee|website=www.paralympic.org|access-date=2016-06-16}}</ref>
